Aikiframework 0.4 php Install
=====================================

1- extract the tar to your server document root and make sure the folder
has script write permissions: 777 ( to create config.php and .htaccess )

2- create an empty database, with collation set to utf8_general_ci.

3- you need PHP 5.1 or above and apache2.

4- mod_rewrite must be enabled inside apache2 httpd.conf

5- visit the document root folder from your browser

6- follow the wizard

7- change the permissions of the folder back to 775

